<li style=3D"font-size:16px; line-height:120%; padding-bottom:8px"><strong>=
Your data control and zero data retention:</strong> Your data is never used=
 for model training or any other purpose. To enhance performance, your inpu=
ts and outputs are used for a speed-up feature called Speculative Decoding.=
 You can disable this at any time by enabling Zero Data Retention (ZDR) in =
