e terms now reflect new capabilities including Role-Based Access Control (R=
BAC) for precise team permissions, options for dedicated endpoints for enha=
nced performance and security, and custom agreements via Order Forms.</li>
<li style=3D"font-size:16px; line-height:120%; padding-bottom:8px"><strong>=
Bring your own models:</strong> The terms now officially support uploading =
your own models and adapters for your private use on our platform. You alwa=
ys retain full ownership and control of your intellectual property.</li>
<li style=3D"font-size:16px; line-height:120%; padding-bottom:8px"><strong>=
Stronger confidentiality guarantees:</strong> We have added a comprehensive=
 Confidentiality clause to provide a stronger legal framework for protectin=
g your sensitive information, offering greater peace of mind for our busine=
ss customers.</li>
</ul>
